OL,3,CBritish Steel electric arc furnace
OL,4,Cplanning permission re-ignites job
OL,5,Cfears
OL,7,FPlans for British Steel to build an
OL,8,Felectric arc furnace at its
OL,9,Fheadquarters have been approved
OL,10,Fsparking fears over job losses.
OL,12,FThe decision by North Council to grant
OL,13,Fplanning permission follows approval
OL,14,Ffor a similar facility at the
OL,15,Fcompany's site on Teeside.
OL,17,FBritish Steel says the #1.25 billion
OL,18,Finvestment is its biggest in more than
OL,19,Fa century and will make the company
OL,20,Fgreen and sustainable.
