OL,4,Cplanning permission re-ignites job
OL,5,Cfears
OL,7,FThe new electric arc furnace would
OL,8,Freplace the two existing coke blast
OL,9,Ffurnaces at the Brigg Road site.
OL,11,FBritish Steel president and CEO Xijun
OL,12,FCao said the company was "extremely
OL,13,Fpleased" to have got the go ahead for
OL,14,Fthe facility.
OL,16,FHe described it as a "significant step
OL,17,Fforward" towards its net zero targets,
OL,18,Fsuggesting the proposed furnaces would
OL,19,Freduce the plant's carbon dioxide
OL,20,Femissions by more than 75 per cent.
