OL,5,Cfears
OL,7,FPreparation work and environmental
OL,8,Fstudies for the project have already
OL,9,Fstarted and British Steel said it
OL,10,Fwould be "delivered at the earliest
OL,11,Fopportunity".
OL,13,FBut unions fear the new furnace could
OL,14,Flead to the loss of 2,000 jobs.
OL,16,FThey wanted the decision deferred to
OL,17,Fenable them to discuss a long term
OL,18,Fplan to become more sustainable
OL,19,Fwithout such a big impact on
OL,20,Femployment.
