OL,7,FMartin Foster from Unite the Union
OL,8,Fsaid: "One of the things that's
OL,9,Fprobably disappointed us more than
OL,10,Fanything is the fact that all this
OL,11,Ftime has passed since the original
OL,12,Fannouncement in probably last October,
OL,13,Fand at no point have we had any proper
OL,14,Fmeaningful consultation meetings with
OL,15,Fthe company.
