OL,7,F"They've simply not sat down with us.
OL,8,FWe could have been sitting down with
OL,9,Fthe company and discussing things and
OL,10,Fprogressing things and trying to come
OL,11,Fup with alternatives that would work
OL,12,Fand would save jobs and protect jobs,
OL,13,Fif not all of them, as many as
OL,14,Fpossible.
OL,16,F"This makes that job really, really
OL,17,Fdifficult now."JLast week a petition
OL,18,Fsigned by 30,000 people was handed to
OL,19,Fpoliticians in Scunthorpe calling for
OL,20,Flong term support for the industry.
